---
title: Crispy Maple Mustard Chicken with Roasted Potato Wedges & Carrots
description: Some say crispy panko-coated chicken is pretty tough to top. Those people clearly don’t know our chefs. They went and made crispy chicken 25x (a scientific number) more delicious by drizzling it with a lick-your-plate-style maple and mustard sauce. On the side, there’s seasoned potato wedges and crispy-edged roasted carrots. The best part? Everything comes together on one baking sheet in under 40 minutes. Because couldn’t we all use a little more time (and fewer dishes to wash)?
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6138dbf36fa6302255622ecb-83827265.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/crispy-maple-mustard-chicken-6138dbf36fa6302255622ecb-72d37668.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/crispy-maple-mustard-chicken-6138dbf36fa6302255622ecb
cuisine: North America
author: Michelle Doll Olson
servings: 2
course: main course
time required: 35 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 650 kcal
  fat: 25 g
  saturated fat: 9 g
